{
 "fragments": [
  {
   "begin": "0.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "6.640", 
   "id": "s000001", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sehr geehrte Frau Pr\u00e4sidentin! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "6.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "9.920", 
   "id": "s000002", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sehr geehrte Damen und Herren! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "9.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "11.760", 
   "id": "s000003", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Liebe Frau Kollegin Bull-Bischoff, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "11.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "13.840", 
   "id": "s000004", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "in Ihrer Rede war viel von Geld die Rede."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "13.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "14.200", 
   "id": "s000005", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "\u2013\u00a0Doch, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "14.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "17.760", 
   "id": "s000006", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie haben ziemlich hohe Milliardenbetr\u00e4ge hier genannt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "17.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "18.320", 
   "id": "s000007", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Geld, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "18.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "23.880", 
   "id": "s000008", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "das auch erst einmal verdient und erarbeitet werden muss und das hier nun ausgegeben werden soll."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "23.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "24.680", 
   "id": "s000009", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich glaube aber, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "24.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "25.360", 
   "id": "s000010", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "meine Damen und Herren, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "25.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "29.480", 
   "id": "s000011", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "es geht bei diesem Thema auch noch um etwas anderes. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "29.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "36.600", 
   "id": "s000012", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die f\u00f6derale Struktur unseres Staates genie\u00dft seit 1949 einen besonderen verfassungsrechtlichen Schutz. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "36.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "41.120", 
   "id": "s000013", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie manifestiert sich nicht zuletzt auch im Bildungswesen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "41.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "44.040", 
   "id": "s000014", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Dass Bildung im Wesentlichen L\u00e4ndersache ist, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "44.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "53.160", 
   "id": "s000015", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "galt dar\u00fcber hinaus \u00fcbrigens schon in der Weimarer Republik und selbst im Kaiserreich."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "53.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "56.280", 
   "id": "s000016", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Lediglich in der Zeit der beiden deutschen Diktaturen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "56.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "61.880", 
   "id": "s000017", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "zur Zeit der Nazidiktatur und zur Zeit der Diktatur der SED, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "61.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "65.080", 
   "id": "s000018", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "haben wir ein zentralistisches Bildungswesen in Deutschland gehabt."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "65.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "65.360", 
   "id": "s000019", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Linke, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "65.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "71.120", 
   "id": "s000020", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "meine Damen und Herren, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "71.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "75.520", 
   "id": "s000021", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "pl\u00e4diert mit dem vorliegenden Antrag f\u00fcr mehr Zentralismus. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "75.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "81.160", 
   "id": "s000022", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Dieses Ziel soll uns mit allerlei populistischem Wortgeklingel schmackhaft gemacht werden. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "81.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "82.600", 
   "id": "s000023", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Bei jedem, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "82.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "86.600", 
   "id": "s000024", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dem unsere Verfassung nicht gleichg\u00fcltig und die Zukunft unserer Kinder wichtig ist, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "86.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "91.640", 
   "id": "s000025", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sollten aber dennoch oder gerade deswegen die Alarmglocken klingen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "91.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "93.760", 
   "id": "s000026", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Zur Vorgeschichte: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "93.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "99.000", 
   "id": "s000027", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Um die teilweise verworrenen Abh\u00e4ngigkeiten zwischen Bund und L\u00e4ndern im Bereich von Bildung und Forschung zu entflechten, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "99.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "101.040", 
   "id": "s000028", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "hat der Bundestag 2006\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "101.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "102.480", 
   "id": "s000029", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "\u00fcbrigens mit gro\u00dfer Mehrheit, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "102.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "104.760", 
   "id": "s000030", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "auch die SPD hat dem zugestimmt\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "104.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "106.920", 
   "id": "s000031", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "eine F\u00f6deralismusreform beschlossen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "106.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "114.320", 
   "id": "s000032", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Dabei wurde die grunds\u00e4tzliche Zust\u00e4ndigkeit der L\u00e4nder f\u00fcr Bildung und Forschung sogar noch bekr\u00e4ftigt. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "114.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "121.720", 
   "id": "s000033", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "F\u00fcr den Bereich der Hochschulen und der Forschung wurde einige Jahre sp\u00e4ter mit der \u00c4nderung des Artikel\u00a091 Grundgesetz, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "121.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "123.600", 
   "id": "s000034", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die 2015 in Kraft trat, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "123.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "128.080", 
   "id": "s000035", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "eine Kooperation von Bund und L\u00e4ndern erleichtert. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "128.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "132.960", 
   "id": "s000036", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Zust\u00e4ndigkeit f\u00fcr die Schulen blieb aber in der Hand der L\u00e4nder; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "132.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "134.520", 
   "id": "s000037", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und das war auch gut so. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "134.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "135.920", 
   "id": "s000038", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Diesen Zustand, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "135.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "141.320", 
   "id": "s000039", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "der in Wahrheit eben nicht erst seit 2006 so oder \u00e4hnlich besteht, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "141.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "147.040", 
   "id": "s000040", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "mit dem politischen Kampfbegriff \u201eKooperationsverbot\u201c zu betiteln, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "147.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "148.200", 
   "id": "s000041", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ist geschickt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "148.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "151.120", 
   "id": "s000042", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wird aber der Sache nicht gerecht."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "151.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "160.560", 
   "id": "s000043", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Der Begriff taucht \u00fcbrigens im Gesetz gar nicht auf."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "160.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "161.960", 
   "id": "s000044", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "In der Sache geht es Ihnen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "161.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "164.040", 
   "id": "s000045", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sehr geehrte Kolleginnen und Kollegen zur Linken, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "164.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "164.680", 
   "id": "s000046", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ja darum, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "164.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "170.360", 
   "id": "s000047", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "auch f\u00fcr den Bereich der Schulen dem Bund zu mehr Einfluss und Geltungsm\u00f6glichkeiten zu verhelfen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "170.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "174.680", 
   "id": "s000048", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Als ob allein dadurch die Bildung schon besser w\u00fcrde."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "174.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "190.920", 
   "id": "s000049", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Gerade im Bereich der Bildung brauchen wir Freiheit und Wettbewerb statt Leistungsabsenkung und Gleichmacherei."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "190.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "192.920", 
   "id": "s000050", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Auch wenn es zun\u00e4chst sinnvoll erscheinen mag, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "192.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "198.360", 
   "id": "s000051", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass der vermeintlich reichere Bund mehr Mittel f\u00fcr die Schulen zur Verf\u00fcgung stellen sollte, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "198.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "202.840", 
   "id": "s000052", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ist der Antrag in dieser Form ein vergiftetes Geschenk; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "202.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "206.480", 
   "id": "s000053", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "denn die Linke will den L\u00e4ndern ja nicht einfach nur mehr Geld geben, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "206.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "207.240", 
   "id": "s000054", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "nein, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "207.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "210.280", 
   "id": "s000055", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sie will sie an den schwarz-rot-goldenen Z\u00fcgel legen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "210.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "210.680", 
   "id": "s000056", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Dem, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "210.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "211.440", 
   "id": "s000057", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "meine Damen und Herren, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "211.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "213.080", 
   "id": "s000058", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "k\u00f6nnen wir nicht zustimmen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "213.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "221.760", 
   "id": "s000059", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Der ideologische Charakter des Antrags wird deutlich, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "221.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "223.760", 
   "id": "s000060", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wenn man sich anschaut, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "223.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "228.600", 
   "id": "s000061", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "welche Vorhaben mit Bundesmitteln finanziert werden sollen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "228.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "233.560", 
   "id": "s000062", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "zum Beispiel die vielgelobte Ganztagsschule. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "233.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "244.720", 
   "id": "s000063", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Nachweislich lassen sich durch Ganztagsschulen keine besseren Bildungsergebnisse erzielen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "244.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "245.640", 
   "id": "s000064", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Dies k\u00f6nnen Sie gerne in der gro\u00dfen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "245.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "248.560", 
   "id": "s000065", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "vom Bildungsministerium selbst gef\u00f6rderten Studie zu den bestehenden Ganztagsschulen nachlesen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "248.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "250.360", 
   "id": "s000066", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Dort steht das alles schwarz auf wei\u00df."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "250.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "252.640", 
   "id": "s000067", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es waren renommierte Institute daran beteiligt. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "252.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "261.720", 
   "id": "s000068", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Interessanterweise hat \u00fcbrigens das Bundesland mit den wenigsten Ganztagsschulen die besten Bildungsergebnisse, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "261.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "263.000", 
   "id": "s000069", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "n\u00e4mlich Bayern."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "263.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "263.600", 
   "id": "s000070", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Schulen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "263.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "269.040", 
   "id": "s000071", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "meine Damen und Herren, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "269.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "277.400", 
   "id": "s000072", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "d\u00fcrfen nach Auffassung der Alternative f\u00fcr Deutschland kein Ort f\u00fcr soziale Experimente oder f\u00fcr die Durchsetzung von Gesellschaftsutopien sein."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "277.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "279.080", 
   "id": "s000073", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "In ihnen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "279.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "280.280", 
   "id": "s000074", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "f\u00fcge ich hinzu, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "280.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "286.640", 
   "id": "s000075", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sollten allein die Vermittlung von Bildung und Wissen im Mittelpunkt stehen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "286.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "288.280", 
   "id": "s000076", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Nicht Marx oder Honecker\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "288.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "289.640", 
   "id": "s000077", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Margot meine ich hier\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "289.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "303.360", 
   "id": "s000078", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "d\u00fcrfen in Bildungsfragen der heimliche Fixstern sein, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "303.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "304.480", 
   "id": "s000079", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sondern Humboldt und Goethe."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "304.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "306.440", 
   "id": "s000080", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wenn es dem Bund tats\u00e4chlich nur darum geht, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "306.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "310.920", 
   "id": "s000081", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die L\u00e4nder allgemein bei der Erf\u00fcllung ihrer Aufgaben im Bereich der Bildung zu unterst\u00fctzen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "310.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "318.840", 
   "id": "s000082", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sollten wir auf die ideologische Selektion bestimmter Projekte verzichten und \u00fcber eine allgemeine F\u00f6rderung bzw. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "318.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "321.840", 
   "id": "s000083", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Entlastung finanzschwacher L\u00e4nder nachdenken\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "321.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "323.240", 
   "id": "s000084", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ich komme gleich zum Ende\u00a0\u2013, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "323.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "327.800", 
   "id": "s000085", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sodass \u00fcber die konkrete Verwendung der Mittel in den L\u00e4ndern selbst entschieden wird. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "327.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "334.480", 
   "id": "s000086", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Eine solche Vorgehensweise entspr\u00e4che eher dem Subsidiarit\u00e4tsprinzip und ist auch demokratischer, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "334.480", 
   "children": [], 
